enb_long_title: United Nations Climate Change Conference - Bali
section_title: DEMONSTRABLE PROGRESS BY ANNEX I PARTIES IN ACHIEVING COMMITMENTS UNDER THE PROTOCOL:
sentences: This issue was discussed and resolved at SBI 26, held in May 2007.
It relates to reports by Annex I parties to demonstrate that they have made progress, by 2005, in achieving their commitments under the Protocol, as required under Protocol Article 3.2.
The COP/MOP adopted the decision forwarded by SBI 26 on 14 December.
